              <h4 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold mb-3">
                Testing
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                A simple test case was created to test if the date of December is generated correctly or not.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center flex-wrap mb-20">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
              <h4 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold mb-3">
                Documentation
              </h4>
              <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
                The doc page (this page) is built with basic Tailwind classes and Twig templates. A controller was created for the url and fucntion. To be simple, Tailwind scripts are directly loaded by CDN insteading of npm building.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
            </div>
          </div>
